<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Tile Probability & Board Position</h2>

<p>Understanding tile distribution helps you anticipate when AZ combinations will appear on your rack. A appears 9 times in the standard 100-tile bag (worth 1 point), while Z appears 1 time (worth 10 points). Together, the AZ pair contributes 11 points before counting any other letters in your word.</p>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
